<section id="content">
	<div class="content-wrap">

		<div class="container clearfix">
			<h1>Who are we?</h1> <h3>We are Coder's Cafe Organization aiming to help <span>all kids</span>&mdash;including special needs and underrepresented groups&mdash;to learn computer science with us!</h3>
		</div>

		<div class="section">
			<div class="container">

				<h1>Our Goals</h1>
				<div class="row col-mb-50">
					<div class="col-md-4">
						<div class="feature-box media-box">
							<div class="fbox-media">
								<img src="/assets/goal0_inclusion.jfif" alt="Goal #1: Inclusion">
							</div>
							<div class="fbox-content px-0">
								<h3>Inclusion<span class="subtitle">To support interested kids and students like you</span></h3>
								<p>We welcome any kids and students who are interested and passionate about computer science to come join with us! People like you are needed more than ever to develop applications to support the changing industry of the dawn of 21st century!</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col-md-4">
						<div class="feature-box media-box flex-column">
							<div class="fbox-media">
								<img src="/assets/goal1_inspire.jfif" alt="Goal #2: Inspire">
							</div>
							<div class="fbox-content px-0">
								<h3>Inspire<span class="subtitle">To foster and grow the interest in computer science</span></h3>
								<p>We guide them to learn and colloborate on variety of different, interesting topics and projects. Show them the many cool and creative projects the world has created. And, motivate them to continue their own, epic journey to see what computer science has to show!</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col-md-4">
						<div class="feature-box media-box flex-column">
							<div class="fbox-media">
								<img src="/assets/goal2_inspect.jfif" alt="Goal #3: Inspect">
							</div>
							<div class="fbox-content px-0">
								<h3>Inspect<span class="subtitle">To expose niche fields in computer science</span></h3>
								<p>Computer science is not just a field of programming, artificial intelligence (AI), data science, or whatever the media is hyping these days. This field has many niche topics that are useful to the world in their own ways!</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="container clearfix">
			<h1>Operations</h1>
			<p>We are currently and only focusing on two operations that best serve the community.</p>

			<div class="row align-items-center col-mb-50">
				<div class="col-md-5">
					<!-- <canvas id="chart-doughnut"></canvas> -->
