					<div class="heading-block border-bottom-0">
						<h4>Programs for Neurodivergent Kids</h4>
						<span>To learn new programming concepts through variety of creative <b>lessons</b> and projects topic by topic.</span>
					</div>

					<p>
						Each programs consists of individual classes, teaching neurodivergent
						students programming and preparing them the 21st century of the growing
						technology sector. We, in partnership with Code the Spectrum, build
						teacher-student connections and flexible curriculums for the neurodivergent students.
					</p>

